(229, 'Re: Favorite Superhero', 'The animated series from the 90''s were the best animated shows ever. You know, back when all the cool shows had some sick ass synth, heavy metal guitar intro.\r\nSpider Man, and Iron Man were definitely among my favorites then. They simply had the sickest intros.\r\n\r\nI do like more Marvel heroes than DC ones, but I only love one of them, Batman.\r\nCyclops has always been my favorite Marvel one, followed closely by Iron Man, but that''s mainly due to Robert Downey.', 226, 9, '2012-07-05 00:43:46', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
