(240, 'Re: The 720', 'I make that out to be rumors.\r\nNever, ever believe anything until Microsoft says It. The internet thing Is plausible, though somewhat unlikely. The used game thing Is just silly. \r\n\r\nThese rumors have been spreading for months, and years. There''s also rumors that the 720 will have Avatar style 3D graphics.\r\n\r\nBut I am skeptic first and foremost at this point. We don''t even know the consoles real name, and people are already making up things It could do.', 239, 9, '2012-07-05 16:42:45', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
(241, 'Re: The 720', 'Yeah, true. It''s just that it was on IGN and I guess that''s what bugged me. They really shouldn''t publish things until they''re 100% sure, that''s why there''s so many rumors. I don''t buy into it either.', 239, 1, '2012-07-05 16:44:55', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
