(263, 'Re: Make way for tildes!', 'Hey, I remember you. Yeah the site thing has been a bit difficult for me lately but Mike had the idea for DreamSpand and I had just been screwed over by my previous web hosts so I offered to build this one on my new web hosts. So far so good. I don''t go by XL anymore though, I''ve pretty much completely started over. CT was fun but it''s long gone. UCG is gone too which is why none of the images there work anymore. \r\n\r\nNice to have you here, and yeah your friends probably won''t be here, sorry, it''s pretty much a new start. Thanks for joining though. :)', 262, 1, '2012-07-07 18:30:41', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
