(564, 'Re: 52 Bests and Worsts of Gaming', '1 - First Video Game You Ever Played\r\n\r\nI think it was Super Mario 64.\r\n\r\n2 - Favorite Classic Game\r\n\r\nMario. :P\r\n\r\n3 - Favorite Current Gen Game\r\n\r\nHalo!\r\n\r\n4 - Favorite Video Game\r\n\r\nThis one is also Halo\r\n\r\n5 - Favorite Console\r\n\r\n360\r\n\r\n6 - Most Comfortable Controller\r\n\r\nPretty much anything EXCEPT the Wii.\r\n\r\n7 - Favorite Hero\r\n\r\nDon''t really have one\r\n\r\n8 - Favorite Heroine\r\n\r\nI derno.\r\n\r\n9 - Favorite Villain\r\n\r\nThe Reapers from Mass Effect\r\n\r\n10 - Best Boss Battle\r\n\r\nI have no idea\r\n\r\n11 - Favorite Supporting Character\r\n\r\nNo clue\r\n\r\n12 - Most Annoying Character\r\n\r\nCortana\r\n\r\n13 - Favorite Couple\r\n\r\nI''m not in to the whole "shipping" thing\r\n\r\n14 - Most Over Rated Game\r\n\r\nCoD\r\n\r\n15 - Most Under Rated Game\r\n\r\nNot sure, F.E.A.R. maybe\r\n\r\n16 - Favorite Genre\r\n\r\nShooters, obviously\r\n\r\n17 - Least Favorite Genre\r\n\r\nAnything stupid\r\n\r\n18 - Game You Hate Admitting You Like\r\n\r\nI don''t think I have any "guilty games." :P except maybe the last installment in The Legend Of Spyro.\r\n\r\n19 - Worst Game You Ever Played\r\n\r\nPretty much any of those movie to game things.\r\n\r\n20 - Best Game You Never Finished\r\n\r\nMajora''s Mask\r\n\r\n21 - Best Gameplay\r\n\r\nIdk\r\n\r\n22. - Worst Gameplay\r\n\r\n- NFS Shift just cause of the way it handles\r\n\r\n23 - Best Graphics\r\n\r\nit''s hard to say\r\n\r\n24 - Worst Graphics\r\n\r\nnot sure\r\n\r\n25 - Best Soundtrack\r\n\r\nHalo\r\n\r\n26 - Best Story\r\n\r\nHalo :p\r\n\r\n27 - Worst Story\r\n\r\nThe NFS games, even though I love the games, their stories suck\r\n\r\n28 - Saddest Scene\r\n\r\nI don''t really find a whole lot of gaming scenes to be sad, except maybe when Admiral Anderson gets shot in ME3\r\n\r\n29 - Best Scene\r\n\r\nIt''s one of those interactive things in ME3, not long after you start playing the game. This lady is like "roar answer my questions you ran away," and if you press RT fast enough, you can punch her. Then Shephard''s like "I''ve had enough of your political bullshit. Stay down." That scene makes me happy. I hate political crap and loved seeing that.\r\n\r\n30 - Best Ending\r\n\r\nI would say Halo, but it never really "ends," so much as it just takes a break for a few years, so Idk.\r\n\r\n31 - Best Cut Scenes\r\n\r\nHalo\r\n\r\n32 - Best Art Style\r\n\r\nI really liked Starfox Adventures.\r\n\r\n33 - Best Voice Acting\r\n\r\nI really like Mass Effect''s voice acting, the way it varies depending on what you say is great, and the actors did a terrific job of putting emotion into their lines.\r\n\r\n34 - Worst Voice Acting\r\n\r\nAn oldish game called Jade Cocoon 2, it was an awesome game but the dialogue sucked\r\n\r\n35 - Best Ensemble Cast\r\n\r\nHaven''t played a lot of those, Spyro was cool though for that\r\n\r\n36 - Best Sequel\r\n\r\nM.E.\r\n\r\n37 - Worst Sequel\r\n\r\nNFS Series, same reason as earlier\r\n\r\n38 - Best "Unknown Game"\r\n\r\nwhat?\r\n\r\n39 - Most Disappointing Game\r\n\r\nHalo Wars\r\n\r\n40 - Most Surprising Game\r\n\r\nI bought AVP out of boredom and it''s actually not too bad of a game\r\n\r\n41 - Three Games You Plan on Playing\r\n\r\ntoo lazy\r\n\r\n42 - A Game You Wish Had a Sequel\r\n\r\nmost of the games I like already do have sequels lol\r\n\r\n43 - A Game You Wish Would Become a Movie\r\n\r\nDo you even have to ask?\r\n\r\n44 - Best RPG\r\n\r\nZelda\r\n\r\n45 - Best FPS\r\n\r\nTough choice.. not sure\r\n\r\n46 - Best Adventure/Action\r\n\r\nNot sure\r\n\r\n47 - Best Puzzle\r\n\r\nPortal\r\n\r\n48 - Best Survival Horror\r\n\r\nTie between F.E.A.R. and Dead Space\r\n\r\n49 - Best TPS\r\n\r\nNo idea?\r\n\r\n50 - Best Sports Game\r\n\r\nI don''t play sports games\r\n\r\n51 - Best Series\r\n\r\nHalo\r\n\r\n52 - Game World You Wished You Could Visit/Live In\r\n\r\nNone lol considering the majority of my games feature hostile aliens or mutated freaks', 562, 1, '2012-09-06 21:56:49', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', 'Changed "ME" to "M.E." so people didn''t get the wrong idea. Lol', ''),
