(608, 'Re: You jerks!', 'Hey Java! It''s been a while. So how''d you get past the limit? Disable JavaScript or what? :p I didn''t really program the character check into the server side but I guess I will now. XD\r\n\r\nI didn''t really "move" anything, it''s a fresh start, for real this time. DreamSpand was Mike''s idea, I just made it a reality. Plus, the people I hosted UCG with randomly doubled their prices on us and I just had enough of it. \r\n\r\nAs far as who''s from CT, well just Mayo, I think, and she''s not on a lot at all. I''ve expanded my horizons on here a bit. This aims at a much bigger audience, and I have a lot of new coding stuff at my disposal that I couldn''t have then. New computer and all that.\r\n\r\nIt''s really good to see ya, man. ', 607, 1, '2012-09-14 22:19:43', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
