(663, 'Re: The Kingdom of the Emerald Castle', '[quote pid=662]\r\n\r\nYes that''s the one. The one the murderous ring dudes ride from.\r\n\r\nInterior shots are here:\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/EMint1_zpsc935b88a.png?t=1348335454[/img]\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is immediately inside. You can see a glimpse of the Bifrost in the center left of the image.\r\n\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint2_zpsc34bd044.png?t=1348335466[/img]\r\n\r\nThe living room. It''s more of a crafting station than anything else.\r\n\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint3_zps31cfaed4.png?t=1348335501[/img]\r\n\r\nThe second floor library/knowledge room. Lots of books, and Ender Chests for effect. Enchanted book in the center, also for effect.\r\n\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint4_zps0d6471bd.png?t=1348335507[/img]\r\n\r\nThird floor. This isn''t anything yet. It''s going to be remodeled at some point.\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emin5_zps840eef1d.png?t=1348335517[/img]\r\n\r\nFourth floor, the Master Bedroom.\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint6_zps5eb51192.png?t=1348336148[/img]\r\n\r\nFourth floor, still the bedroom.\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint7_zpsd56e5f58.png?t=1348336184[/img]\r\n\r\nView from the accidentally built Fifth floor balcony.\r\n\r\n[img]http://i1195.photobucket.com/albums/aa387/SamAxe92/Emint8_zps6e37492f.png?t=1348336239[/img]\r\n\r\nSame balcony, showing the small village below the Castle. I am going to expand the village, as well as the docks.\r\nI''m hoping to add Viking longboats to the docks as well, once I figure out the best way to build them.', 655, 9, '2012-09-22 17:27:22', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 9, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
