(788, 'Re: Critique Uncle Java''s Ridiculous Songs!', 'Well, first off I wouldn''t call Skrillex Dubstep. XD He''s more like electro-step, trust me, Jennie and I talked about that haha. It''s funny lol I''ll give ya that. It does sound pretty cool, and maybe it''s just not my taste but it''s like.. Idk, dry or something. I''m used to harder stuff than that, so I''m probably a bit biased. Definitely better than anyone else though, you know what you''re doing, so it''s probably just my taste.\n\nMight make good sex music. XD Like you and your mate are in bed and you''re like "Here''s the part of my body that it''s talking about!"', 786, 1, '2012-10-05 19:23:27', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
