(798, 'Re: 52 Bests and Worsts of Gaming', ' 1- First Video Game You Ever Played\r\n[b]For console, Super Mario All-Stars. If PC counts, then Space Cadet Pinball[/b]\r\n\r\n2 - Favorite Classic Game\r\n[b]...Too many to count XD, being a retro junkie and all[/b]\r\n\r\n3 - Favorite Current Gen Game\r\n[b]Okami for Nintendo Wii[/b]\r\n\r\n4 - Favorite Video Game\r\n[b]Hard to say... probably SA2B[/b] \r\n\r\n\r\n5 - Favorite Console\r\n[b]a tie between SNES and Gamecube[/b]\r\n\r\n6 - Most Comfortable Controller\r\n[b]Gamecube hands down[/b]\r\n\r\n7 - Favorite Hero\r\n[b]too many favourites... Luigi, Yoshi, Kirby, Rayman or Earthworm Jim[/b]\r\n\r\n8 - Favorite Heroine\r\n[b]Jade or Okami Amaterasu[/b]\r\n\r\n9 - Favorite Villain\r\n[b]Fawful, K. Rool, or Gruntilda[/b]\r\n\r\n10 - Best Boss Battle\r\n[b]Baby Bowser from Yoshi''s Island, Gruntilda from Banjo Kazooie, Yami from Okami, Cackletta from mario and luigi: super star saga[/b]  \r\n\r\n11 - Favorite Supporting Character\r\n[b] Issun, Yoshi or Luma[/b]\r\n\r\n12 - Most Annoying Character\r\n[b]Chip, Navi, Omochao, pretty much anything that is small, flies around and gives obvious information[/b]\r\n\r\n13 - Favorite Couple\r\n[b]None of them :P[/b] \r\n\r\n14 - Most Over Rated Game\r\n[b]Call of Duty[/b]\r\n\r\n15 - Most Under Rated Game\r\n[b]I''ve played quite few games that I''d consider underrated, Beyond Good and Evil, Maui Mallard, Billy Hatcher, Crystal Chronicles for the DS[/b]\r\n\r\n16 - Favorite Genre\r\n[b]Platformer[/b]\r\n\r\n17 - Least Favorite Genre\r\n[b] one-on-one fighters and FPS[/b]\r\n\r\n18 - Game You Hate Admitting You Like\r\n[b]Donkey Konga, Conker''s Pocket Tales[/b]\r\n\r\n19 - Worst Game You Ever Played\r\n[b]Minan: Everyday Hero, Tamagotchi Corner Shop[/b]\r\n\r\n20 - Best Game You Never Finished\r\n[b]Probably all the those Legend of Zelda titles which none of them are completed[/b]  \r\n\r\n21 - Best Gameplay\r\n[b]Donkey Kong Country 2[/b]\r\n\r\n22. - Worst Gameplay\r\n[b]Superman 64[/b] \r\n\r\n23 - Best Graphics\r\n[b]Paper Mario, Kirby Epic Yarn and Okami, I don''t judge graphics by how realistic they are, but how creative they are. Realistic graphics just seem overdone to me. [/b] \r\n\r\n24 - Worst Graphics\r\n[b]Any Atari game[/b]\r\n\r\n25 - Best Soundtrack\r\n[b]Castle Crashers, Donkey Kong Country, a good proportion of Sonic games[/b]\r\n\r\n26 - Best Story\r\n[b]Beyond Good and Evil, Gravity Bone[/b]\r\n\r\n27 - Worst Story\r\n[b]Muscle March[/b]\r\n\r\n28 - Saddest Scene\r\n[b]any scene where a likable character dies, really[/b]\r\n\r\n29 - Best Scene\r\n[b]personally for me, when Luigi dresses up as Peach in Superstar Saga[/b]\r\n\r\n30 - Best Ending\r\n[b]Not too sure... Banjo Tooie''s ending always amused me[/b]\r\n\r\n31 - Best Cut Scenes\r\n[b]best cut scene styles would include Sonic and the Secret Rings, and Okami[/b]\r\n\r\n32 - Best Art Style\r\n[b]Okami[/b]\r\n\r\n33 - Best Voice Acting\r\n[b]Never really noticed any good voice acting[/b]\r\n\r\n34 - Worst Voice Acting\r\n[b]House of the dead[/b]\r\n\r\n35 - Best Ensemble Cast\r\n[b]I dunno[/b]\r\n\r\n36 - Best Sequel\r\n[b]Donkey Kong Country 2[/b]\r\n\r\n37 - Worst Sequel\r\n[b]all those pointless Angry Birds remakes[/b]\r\n\r\n38 - Best "Unknown Game"\r\n[b]Beyond Good and Evil[/b]\r\n\r\n39 - Most Disappointing Game\r\n[b]That recent-ish Duke Nukem game[/b]\r\n\r\n40 - Most Surprising Game\r\n[b]Muscle March, Rayman[/b]\r\n\r\n41 - Three Games You Plan on Playing\r\n[b]Paper Mario: Sticker Star, Pokemon White 2 or Black 2, Rayman Legends[/b]\r\n\r\n42 - A Game You Wish Had a Sequel\r\n[b]Beyond Good and Evil, an actual Banjo Three-ie, and Conker''s Bad Fur Day[/b]\r\n\r\n43 - A Game You Wish Would Become a Movie\r\n[b]...part of me thinks Conker''s Bad Fur Day (lol), but if the movie could actually be done well, then something from the Mario universe[/b]\r\n\r\n44 - Best RPG\r\n[b]Pokemon, Paper Mario TTYD, or Mario + Luigi Superstar Saga[/b]\r\n\r\n45 - Best FPS\r\n[b]Banjo Tooie''s multiplayer mode[/b]\r\n\r\n46 - Best Adventure/Action\r\n[b]Okami[/b]\r\n\r\n47 - Best Puzzle\r\n[b]Tetris, or Mario & Yoshi[/b]\r\n\r\n48 - Best Survival Horror\r\n[b]never played those[/b]\r\n\r\n49 - Best TPS (Third Person Shooter)\r\n[b]Earthworm Jim, Gunstar Heros, Maui Mallard[/b]\r\n\r\n50 - Best Sports Game\r\n[b]don''t really play these either[/b]\r\n\r\n51 - Best Series\r\n[b]Donkey Kong Country, paper Mario, Rayman and Pokemon[/b]\r\n\r\n52 - Game World You Wished You Could Visit/Live In\r\n[b]POKEYMAN! actually I take that back...\r\nSONIC UNIVERSE!!! *jumps into Chao Transporter*[/b]\r\n\r\nk im done', 562, 15, '2012-10-06 04:09:23', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 15, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
