(855, 'Re: Damn 360.', 'I''m just worried that they''re gonna tell me the same thing, that it can''t be repaired because of the seal being broken.\n\nAnd on a site note, yeah, you got a point about that. I was GOING to take summer classes online, programming classes even, and use that knowledge here. They initially told my family and I that "they''re cheaper." Now with the Pell Grant, we''d only been paying like, $94 for the quarters, one class in the second quarter really spiked it to almost a hundred dollars more than that, but that was because it was a CPR class (that I''m certified in). Well, after much running around with heads cut off, we finally came to time to pay for the classes. They wanted FIVE hundred dollars for that, and somehow that was cheaper. This was the same lady that told us that, too.\n\nSo now I gotta choose between the 360 or school and I really don''t have much of a choice in that, I''m gonna have to choose the latter.', 724, 1, '2012-10-07 22:09:41', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
