(987, 'Re: Scary Games', 'Anything from the Silent Hill series will probably give you a decent case of the jibblies. Now here''s one you''ve probably not played....but I recommend you do if you can get your hands on it:\r\n\r\nClocktower (PS1). It''s technically the 2nd game of the series but #1 never came out in America. So Japan''s Clocktower 2 is what we know as simply, "Clocktower". It''s a minimal horror game with a fun story. It''s not that long of a play either, maybe...3 hours tops? Has multiple endings and all that good stuff. It''s pretty fun and worth at least a single play-through.\r\n\r\nNow if you can only find Clocktower 3 (PS2).....just say no. It''s horrifying, but in a totally different sense. It''s SCARY how bad it sucks haha.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Metroid Prime, another great survival horror game hahaha', 980, 23, '2012-10-16 22:41:39', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 23, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
