(995, 'I made stuff', 'I used to toy around with 3-D animation a few years back. It would take me hours to render out a scene just a few seconds long. I did have more luck with still images. Here are a few of them. I made these using a program called Bryce 5. I currently have no plans to continue working with the program, but who knows what will happen when I get bored. I usually did enviroment shots, as that is what the program is built for, but I did dabble in lighting effects right before quitting the program.\r\n\r\n[center][img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/alaskamountain.jpg[/img][/center]\r\n\r\n[center][img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/snowmount2.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\n[img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/desertmountain.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\n[u]Lighting Tests[/u]\r\n\r\n[i]First Attempt[/i]\r\n[img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/bump.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\n[i]2nd Attempt[/i]\r\n[img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/light.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\n[i]3rd and Final Attempt[/i]\r\n[img]http://i984.photobucket.com/albums/ae324/solidbatman/Bryce%205/redglassground.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nThe above image took 7 hours total to make and I was not happy at all with the way it turned out, thus making me quit the program all together and learning photoshop instead. Anyway, hope you guys enjoyed. I have a few more that I may add later.', 995, 16, '2012-10-17 03:03:14', 46, 'no', ':2:16:9:1:1:1:1:2:2:2:2:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:2:1:1:12:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:55', 'I is artist. Van Gogh cut his ear off for me', '2012-11-02 21:20:53', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 145, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
(996, 'Re: I made stuff', 'Wow. Dude, those look so flippin'' real. I''ve always been interested in 3D modeling but have never been any good at it. Nice job.', 995, 1, '2012-10-17 03:06:22', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
