(1779, 'Re: February Top Ten', 'Solidbatman, i think it is time for you to stop bashing Call of Dooty. Listen, i understand you do not like it, i understand that you are not good at it, i understand that your mom keeps having sex with other players, but that does not give you the excuse to bash the game. Call of Duty is a marvelous game, with marvelous graphics, and high-tense battles. Each CoD game is better than the last with more explosions and slightly better graphics. Yes, a lot of kids play it, but who cares? Remember when you were a kid? When you were playing games? Remember how you used to bash people older than you and call them n00bs? They are going through this same stage. So let them be, let them have fun, let them be gamers. \r\n\r\nBut i have to agree with Alpha, ill take Halo over this any day. Halo is like...life. So many choices you can make to get to the same ending. Want to complete a vehicle mission on foot? Do it. Want to steal enemy vehicles? Do it. Want to use a warthog, put a guy on the machine gun and equip someone with a rocket and have them fire a volley from the passenger seat? Do it. ', 1773, 34, '2013-03-15 12:51:08', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
