(1699, 'Re: Xbox Event ', '[quote pid=1698]\r\n\r\nOh, and maybe get some worthwhile exclusives. Xbox has 3 main exclusives; Halo, Gears of War, and Forza where Sony has a heck of a lot more, even from third party guys. If Microsoft wants to keeps its lead over Sony (which Sony closed the gap tremendously), it will have to reel in some solid third part exclusive developers.\r\n\r\nMicrosoft can put all the cool gizmos they want on the system, but unless I see some cool new exclusive IPs, then I''ll feel worse about it than I did the PS4 announcements. In short, whatever Persona 5 comes out on will be bought by me.  \r\n\r\n ', 1686, 16, '2013-02-25 18:15:27', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
