(1702, 'Re: Xbox Event ', '[img]http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1xSGP-OJZww/TahCmeRC-WI/AAAAAAAAASs/T5yqqEmIlrE/s1600/Rei%2Bstops%2BAsuka.JPG[/img]\r\n\r\nFirst off, Halo is a great game. It rises in the heavens alongside NieR, resting in the hands of Yuko, taking care of the above hereafter. God of War is a solid game, i have to give it its credit, so do you. And yes, Microsoft indeed is a tad bit low on the exclusive sides...but does that matter? Even if it does...xbox is way more popular than the PS3...just saying. But it is as you said, it is in the eye of the beholder, but wish i can say the same about Natsume...but in this special case, i dont think anyone wants to look at that. and this is a fact. but you are certainly right about how amazing Natsume is. I bow to your obvious superiority in opinion and taste and will always agree with you or I will allow you to ban me.\r\n\r\nEdit: [s]Solidbatman, i think it is safe to say that [s]I[/s] you won this you [s]cheating Natsume[/s]incredible human being![/s]\r\n\r\nEdit: Alpha...i think you need to disable solidbatman''s ability to modify other people''s post', 1686, 34, '2013-02-26 03:47:02', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 34, 0, '', '', 'no', '', 'ante baka Solidbatman!', ''),
(1703, 'Re: Xbox Event ', '[img]http://i92.photobucket.com/albums/l37/Corporeal/e37a98ec.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nIt still connected. Asuka: 1 Rei: 0 (Which Rei are we on now? Rei III or something?)\r\n\r\n Xbox is popular 1)because it had a year long head start. In term of worldwide sales, PS3 leads in Europe and freaking destroys Xbox in Japan where the Xbox is more of a joke than anything. Of course, we must all bow down to what the Wii did to both of them.\r\n\r\nIt went god-mode\r\n\r\n[img]http://tsuzukusekai.files.wordpress.com/2011/06/eva_third_impact.jpg?w=640&h=360[/img]\r\n\r\n\r\n(In case you are wondering, yes. Vibrantblade and I actually argue using shows as metaphors. Also Asuka>Rei) ', 1686, 16, '2013-02-26 04:02:51', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
(1704, 'Re: Xbox Event ', '[img]http://www.nervarchives.com/images/icon.200x150.wings.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nMust i remind you what happens at this part? Yeah...the part right after she thought she beat them. To be perfectly honest, it is one of my favorite scenes in the whole series. \r\n\r\nThe only reason why it is a joke in Japan is due to its poor amount of JRPGs. Sony remains strong in Japan for this very reason. Which honestly, is the best reason to get a Sony system. So yeah you are right, it is all about the exclusives. But hey, the xbox vs PS3 argument is old and useless. They both have their uses. Once the Xbox720 event comes and passes, we shall discuss the next generation of consoles. \r\n\r\n[img]http://i20.photobucket.com/albums/b234/kidd_0218/Rei_Ayanami_-_000.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nAsuka:1   Rei:Infinite ', 1686, 34, '2013-02-26 10:34:41', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 34, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
(1705, 'Today is a special day...', 'Alright, so today is the 26th day of the 2nd month of the 2013th year since Jesus walked these lands. What does that mean? It means, that today is Tuesday! Yup! The day right after Monday, the dreadful day of the week! As we fully adjust to the new week, I take it upon myself to remind you all to remember. Remember the times you stayed up late playing your games. Remember the times you threw your controller across the room after failing 10 times to beat a mission. Remember the times when you roared in triumph, as you beat said mission, All those tears of joy and sadness. But above all, remember this. Remember Reach. Remember the great planet and its beauty before the Covenant onslaught. Remember the forces that died to their last breath, to protect the place, to protect the universe, to protect Earth and all of its colonies. So go about your day, with this in mind. If you are a soldier, remember that we are with you in spirit, just like how we were with the population of Reach. When you return, you shall be welcomed with open arms and our full support. So salute all personnel, current and past, when you see them, assure them that they are in our prayers, just like the soldiers of Reach. And if you see a veteran, lend them support, for they need it. So i bid ye, Dreamspand, to have an enjoyable Tuesday. \r\n\r\nOh...today is also Solidbatman''s birthday. \r\n\r\n\r\n[img]http://24.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mcz1sw26lb1qmouyyo1_500.jpg[/img]', 1705, 34, '2013-02-26 14:26:32', 46, 'no', ':16:1:9:1:34:2:1:1:2:1:1:12:1:1:42:1:5:1:1:1:1:1:55', '...to die!', '2013-03-02 05:58:13', 0, 0, 0, 0, 34, 95, '', '', 'no', '', 'forgot to add an important bit', ''),
(1706, 'Re: Xbox Event ', 'Ok, so in the end neither one wins and merely come back, "rebuild" and repeat it all over again. Sony and Microsoft will continue to battle for our attention until the cycle is broken. \r\n\r\n\r\n[img]http://i65.photobucket.com/albums/h204/jedinewtype/vlcsnap-704103.png[/img]\r\n\r\n[img]http://wiki.evageeks.org/images/2/23/M26_C478_d_Choking_my_Asuka.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nSony and Microsoft are doomed to be rivals for our love until we decide which we really want to have. \r\n\r\n[img]http://crymore.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/rei-asuka.jpg[/img]\r\n\r\nand dont bring MPE scene up. It still hurts me to watch that :(', 1686, 16, '2013-02-26 15:13:37', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 16, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
