(2076, 'The Time Has Come', 'The time has come. We were promised this day 4 long years ago, way back in 2009. I was only 16 then. I had my first car, was running cross country, and forgot that Vibrantblade even went to my school (to be fair, he isn''t very noticeable). In those 4 years, many things have happened. I graduated high school, I''ve gone through 2 jobs, Steve Jobs died (#neverforget), Kony got away, and The Dark Knight Rises was released.\r\nI am freaking excited to share this news, that only one other member here will actually care about. \r\n\r\n[i]Rebuild of Evangelion: 3.33 You Can (Not) Redo[/i] comes out on 7 days and Studio Khara put together this pretentious, kick ass, trailer for it.\r\n\r\n[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldsyUTnEUqo]WATCH THIS FOR CONFUSION[/url]\r\n\r\n[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fS26Hw9_L38]Awesome 6 Minute Preview[/url]', 2076, 16, '2013-04-17 20:06:04', 46, 'no', ':16:34:2:1:1:1:1:1:1:55', 'It is nearly upon us', '2013-04-18 02:42:52', 0, 0, 0, 0, 16, 97, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
