(1870, 'The Minecraft Server', 'I talked about this with Alpha the other night, and I think it''s pretty important to air this idea to everyone; Our Minecraft server has massive potential.\r\n\r\nI''m thinking we could try and raise activity through the server, and have one huge opening project for the website.\r\nWe can all pitch in some suggestions for something that would be fun, interesting and attention grabbing we can all build as a team on the server.\r\n\r\nThoughts?', 1870, 9, '2013-03-20 16:25:10', 46, 'no', ':34:16:9:1:2:1:1:1:1:1:55', 'N/A', '2013-04-07 14:45:23', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 272, ':1', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
