(1873, 'Re: The Minecraft Server', '[quote pid=1871]I''d have to talk to Mike, but please understand that right now, it''s very hard for either one of us to pay for anything extra. Both of us are struggling to keep houses and vehicles, and we''re both going through a lot of loss.\n\nI like the idea a lot, but I''m afraid you''d have to pay for at least most of it. Still though, it''s ultimately up to him as it''s his server and all that. I actually sent him something earlier about finding an online server. The only problem is that he has a contract with Hamachi for a year already, so we''d have to find a few workarounds for that. Other that, I say yeah, you got my vote for this.', 1870, 1, '2013-03-20 17:13:40', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
