(1892, 'The official "I am on the MC Server" Thread.', 'Rather than constantly having to update your status, or only send PM''s to selected members, in this thread everyone can just shout out whenever they''re on the Dreamspands Minecraft server, and maybe is feeling a little lonely, and then whoever feels like they''re being way to productive, can join in for some creative fun and banter.\r\n\r\nI''ll start off, I''m online now and could really use a hand or two.\r\n', 1892, 9, '2013-03-21 22:13:12', 46, 'no', ':1:16:2:1:14:55:55:5', 'Dreamspands Minecraft Server.', '2013-05-26 20:22:21', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 249, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
(1904, 'Server Rules', 'We hope you''re enjoying our Official DreamSpand Gaming Minecraft Server. However, we must inform you that rules do apply:\r\n\r\n1. [b]No killing any cats or dogs[/b] unless you absolutely have no other choice. They may be pets of some of the users, and animals do escape.\r\n\r\n2. [b]No spawn egg abuse of any kind[/b] which includes but is not limited to: spawning multiple entities of the same mob, several different mobs, spawning them then killing them, or using chicken eggs to rapidly spawn chickens. There is enough lag without this and we are already in the process of adding in a plugin to remove mobs upon command. If you are caught doing this, you will be temporarily kicked from the server until further notice. If this remains an issue, you will be permanently kicked. [b]Spawn eggs are temporarily disabled and should not spawn anything anyway, but slips can be made.[/b]\r\n\r\n3. [b]DO NOT destroy someone else''s work[/b] or modify it without their permission. You can help others, but destroying someone else''s work (or changing something you don''t like) is just plain rude and obnoxious. This will not be tolerated. You may, however, build whatever you like, wherever you like, so long as it doesn''t conflict with other creations.\r\n\r\n4. [b]Follow the rules of DreamSpand itself.[/b] Just because you''re on the server doesn''t mean that the regular rules don''t apply.\r\n\r\n5. [b]Do not cause any unnecessary lag[/b] such as high-powered/multiple redstone clocks (one or two is okay if used correctly), loads of TNT, turning the lighting systems on and off repeatedly, placing spawners, etc. Every now and then with permission from the staff is okay, but all the time on your own accord is intolerable.\r\n\r\n6. [b]No killing other players or setting another player''s spawn point[/b]. This includes teleporting them to 0, 0, 0, and failure to abide by these will result in you being de-opped (if you were/are an op).\r\n\r\n7. [b]Don''t clear another player''s inventory[/b] unless they ask you to. It''s just plain wrong.\r\n\r\nOver all, have fun. The server gives us a unique aspect that not a lot of places have, and we would like to keep it a terrestrial environment as much as possible. It''s meant to be fun and amazing, so let''s try to keep it that way. Enjoy, and game on.', 1904, 1, '2013-03-22 14:24:43', 46, 'no', ':1:2:14:1:49:1:1:34:1:1:9:1:1:1:55:55', 'Follow these here rules, yo.', '2013-03-22 14:24:43', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135, '', '', 'no', 'minecraft, server, rules, forum, dreamspand', '', ''),
