(1906, 'How To Change Your Minecraft Skin', 'If you''ve been on the server for a bit, then you''ve noticed that the majority of us have different skins than the typical ''Steve'' look. Changing your look is quick and easy!\r\n\r\n[b]Instructions[/b]\r\n\r\n1. Go to http://www.planetminecraft.com/\r\n\r\n2. Click on the "Skins" button/link.\r\n\r\n3. You can browse these skins for ones you might like, or you can type what you would like to search for in the search bar up top (beneath the PLANET MINECRAFT logo).\r\n\r\n4. Once you find a skin you like, click on the link to open it up. A box may pop up asking you if you want to run this application, just select [b]Yes[/b].\r\n\r\n5. Click on Change My Skin and you will be redirected to http://www.minecraft.net/\r\n\r\n6. If you''re not logged in, then do so and it will probably send you back to the homepage. If this is the case, simply click on Change My Skin again.\r\n\r\n7. Once you''re to the page that asks you if you''re sure if you want to change your skin, simply click the button that says [b]Change[/b].\r\n\r\n8. If you''re currently playing Minecraft, then exit the client and rejoin for the looks to take effect.\r\n\r\nThere! Now you have your very own look!', 1906, 1, '2013-03-22 14:37:52', 46, 'no', ':1:9:2:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:1:55:55', 'Instructions on how to change your look.', '2013-03-22 14:37:52', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 77, '', '', 'no', 'minecraft, server, skin, change, instructions, planet', '', ''),
