(2003, 'Re: Minecraft Server Control Room', 'Okay.\n\nScrew it being open to the public. This is why I don''t trust people. The public is nothing but a long list of faggots and trolls with nothing but disrespect and childish behavior. I had the server on the PMC server list for no longer than FIVE MINUTES and I had people come on that were spamming the server, one guy that was disrespectful.. I think only ONE person on there was a decent, non-grieving member, and he left a minute or two after joining. Server is back on the white-list, and that is where it is going to [b]stay[/b]. I had someone use multiple accounts to get out of a ban, even. These worlds were are the result of our hard work and progress and I am not going to let an immature, dumbass child ruin it for us. ', 1940, 1, '2013-04-07 19:44:13', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
