(2005, 'Re: Minecraft Server Control Room', 'Unfortunately, yes.\n\nAnyway, the Nether portal for the survival map does not seem to be working. Also, I just noticed (and Jean did too) that no hostile mobs are spawning in the survival map all of a sudden, either. I don''t know what''s going on, but hopefully we can get this sorted out tomorrow. This ain''t makin no sense. :/\n\nedit: Nevermind about the mobs. I got em to spawn again.', 1940, 1, '2013-04-08 04:10:27', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
