(2031, 'Re: The Three Kingdoms', 'I''m thinking, in the Snowmens description it mentions a war, I think that war could have been like World War 1 for this map. It was huge, lots of people died and it changed everything.\r\n\r\nSo, in a huge conflict like that maybe all the kingdoms that we didn''t choose might have been too weak as a nation to compete with the bigger kingdoms (the ones we did select), and as such they had to seek refuge with one of the three kingdoms that exists now.\r\nAs a result of this, the Kingdoms adopted several cultural feats from the kingdoms they offered refuge.\r\n\r\nThoughts?', 2023, 9, '2013-04-11 15:32:26', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
