(2037, 'Re: Minecraft Server Control Room', 'Since "Generate Structures" was turned off for the survival map, there are things that won''t get spawned in it, such as strongholds, villages, temples, or mineshafts. Therefore, I will take it upon myself to go into creative mode and randomly make structures and chests with rare items in them. This way things can still be leveled out. I probably will make some villages, too.\n\nedit: Welp, made two villages and a small stronghold. Of course, after I go through the trouble of doing that, I find a naturally spawning village in the desert. =__= So generate structures are definitely turned on. But enjoy the make-shift stuff anyway.', 1940, 1, '2013-04-12 18:39:04', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
(2038, 'Re: The Three Kingdoms', 'I am proud to present you, the map for our Kingdom world. Circled, are the areas i think will be the best place to put the central area of the respected kingdom. Those areas will give the best distance between other kingdoms and the village. LEt me know what you guys think. \r\n\r\nOh and just to double check:\r\n\r\nSammy will do the Woodsman Kingdom\r\nPaul will do the Snowman Kingdom\r\nMike will do the Miner Kingdom\r\n\r\ncorrect?\r\n\r\n[img]http://i.imgur.com/u6IfUxQ.jpg[/img]', 2023, 34, '2013-04-13 00:45:36', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
