(2049, 'Server Ideas', 'Okay, so there are a couple of ideas I''ve had for the server for a bit.\r\n\r\nFirst off, I was thinking we could allow members access to the server for a certain amount of tokens. What this amount will cost has yet to be decided, and unless I can use the SQL database to automatically add people to the white-list (which would be freaking awesome), we''ll have to approve/disapprove of them once they request it.\r\n\r\nSecondly, I was thinking about ''selling'' some items for the survival map on the forums, using the tokens. For example, there could be different "shop" threads for different types of items, and they could either be ridiculously expensive or relatively cheap. This way, if someone has a decent amount of tokens, they can buy starting gear without having to ask others for it.\r\n\r\nLet me know what you think. This should add some compatibility between the forums and the server, I think.', 2049, 1, '2013-04-13 16:14:50', 46, 'no', ':9:1:2:1:1:1:1:1:55', 'Post ideas for the server here.', '2013-04-13 16:18:45', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 42, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
