(2056, 'Re: The Three Kingdoms', 'I think we should make some simple puzzle dungeons ourselves. Nothing big, just a few tripwire traps and some basic loot. I saw plenty of good locations on the map.\r\n\r\nYeah the Junglers seemed like the natural bad guys for me, though at the beginning of the story in game they won''t actually be there.\r\nI''ve made a deeper sub-plot with them to explain their reasons for attacking, as well as explaining a boss fight.\r\n\r\nAnd perfect friggin'' name Alpha, love it.\r\n\r\nI''d quite like to refine it a bit, and make it more official like, the versions i post here are just rough cuts to iron out the plots and such.', 2023, 9, '2013-04-14 14:40:13', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
