(2062, 'Re: The Three Kingdoms', 'Sammy! Forgot all about you! The Kingdoms world has been completed, and it is time for everyone to build their respected kingdoms. Earlier on in this post, i posted a pic with circled areas. These show where i think is the best place for everyone to build their kingdoms. So you can go on anytime and start building in the forest Biome. I think right next to a river is best, which is marked. There are 2 sections of a kingdom. Main one is the Central Castle. This area will be the center of the kingdom and most important. Only citizens of that kingdom are allowed in, so shops will be located there. Next Section is the lands of your citizens. This is where most of your citizens will live. Anyone can go there, but only citizens can build. They can build/mine/cut/do their jobs/ do whatever there. Then everywhere else in the biome is part of your kingdom. build watchtowers, build supply depots, refreshment depots, up to you. it is yours, but keep to the theme. \r\n\r\n', 2023, 34, '2013-04-15 13:05:35', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
