(2148, 'Re: So.', 'The reason the server is down is because you updated to 1.5.2 and our server is 1.5.1. A new CraftBukkit file has to be released first before it can be played on.\r\n[quote pid=2136]\r\nI''m really getting tired of this "I''m not posting until he does" crap. From now on, if anyone thinks like that, they''re off the staff. Period. I want people that are gonna try, regardless of if anyone else is or not. Look guys, I''ve really tried being nice and understanding and clearly it''s not working. I am sorry for this, but I want you guys to post. Sam''s started and is doing a good job, so why can''t anyone else? Mike posted a little bit and for that I am grateful. Thank you both for trying so hard, I really appreciate that and if there''s a way I can show that, please tell me and I will be happy to oblige.\r\n\r\nJust post anyway guys, stop waiting for someone else, I mean it. Changes will be made if I don''t see posts being made.', 2132, 1, '2013-05-02 20:03:19', 46, 'yes', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
