(2279, 'Attack on Titan', 'There is an anime airing right now that has done something only the rare anime can do. Have a nearly universal opinion that its incredible. This season, we are being treated to one of the grittiest, most epic, masterfully animated shows I have ever seen. \r\n\r\nThis show is called Attack on Titan. \r\n\r\nI know anime has a stereotype of being all about underage panty shots or big eyed, cutely drawn girls. Aside from being flat out wrong, Attack on Titan is not what you think of when you first think of anime. \r\n\r\nThe story tells of humanity, forced to live inside a series of walls in order to survive against Titans, giant humanoid creatures that only live to destroy humanity. Eren is a young man living inside the walls who knows that eventually, the walls will be broken, and Titans will devour the remnants of humanity. He wants to take the fight to the Titans before that can happen.\r\n\r\nAttack on Titan has the most twists and turns I''ve seen from any anime in a long time. This isn''t an anime, its a non-stop supply of adrenaline being shot into you. It gets your heart pounding and hooks you, making you beg for more after each episode. \r\n\r\nMy previous attempts at getting you guys into anime haven''t worked out all that great, but this show is unlike anime I''ve ever seen, and I''ve seen around 100 different anime. \r\n\r\nHere, have a kick ass trailer that covers the first 6 episodes. [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1aIlbGiM8lk]Trailer[/url]. \r\n\r\nTrust me, this show is just amazing.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in watching this action packed adrenaline rush, let me know and I can hook you up with downloads or a membership to stream it online. ', 2279, 16, '2013-05-29 00:06:33', 46, 'no', ':16:9:2:1:34:1:55', 'You really really really need to watch this show.', '2013-05-29 00:06:33', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 83, '', '', 'no', '', '', ''),
