(2291, 'How To Join The Tekkit Server', 'Looking to join our Tekkit Minecraft server? No problem! Just follow the steps below. You''ll be surviving with us in no time.\r\n\r\n[b]Note: [/b] For right now, the server is white-listed. If you would still like to join, PM a staff member and simply request access.\r\n\r\n[b]IMPORTANT: [/b] To join our server, you will need the [b]ExtraBiomesXL[/b] and [b]Project Zulu[/b] mods in your mods folder. Please click [url=mods/ExtrabiomesXL-universal-1.5.2-3.13.4.jar]here[/url] to download ExtraBiomesXL, and click [url=mods/ProjectZuluCompletev1.0.3.8.zip]here[/url] to download Project Zulu.\r\n\r\n[b]**[/b] Once downloaded, navigate to %appdata% -> .technic -> tekkitmain -> mods and save it there. After that just restart your launcher and you''re good. Note that new biomes only generate in new chunks, so if you find one close by, good job, but mostly they''re far away - this goes for some new mobs as well.\r\n\r\n[b] HOW TO JOIN THE SERVER ITSELF [/b]\r\n\r\n1. Download the [url=http://www.technicpack.net/download]Technic Launcher[/url] for Tekkit.\r\n\r\n2. Once it comes up, click on the [b]Launch[/b] button. This can take a few minutes, especially the first time.\r\n\r\n3. Tekkit will be stuck on the MOJANG screen for a little bit. You should only be worried if it says "Not Responding," in which case you just need to close it and restart it. It will lag a little bit. This is completely normal.\r\n\r\n4. Once the Minecraft main screen pops up, click on [b]Multiplayer[/b].\r\n\r\n5. Click on [b]Add Server[/b].\r\n\r\n6. In the [b]Server Address[/b] field, type [b]74.63.213.50:47407[/b].\r\n\r\n7. Type "DreamSpand Gaming" into the [b]Server Name[/b] field. ** Optional\r\n\r\n8. Click on the [b]Done[/b] button.\r\n\r\nThe server should pop up saying something like 0/50 (any number of players can be on at a time, however). The description should just simply say A Tekkit server. If you see that, then congrats! You''ve added the server correctly! Click it to select it and then click on [b]Join Server[/b]. Have fun.\r\n\r\n** Not working? Post a topic about it!', 2291, 1, '2013-06-21 17:43:41', 66, 'no', ':1:9:2:14:49:1:44:5:55:55', 'Instructions on how to join our Tekkit Minecraft server.', '2013-06-21 17:43:41', 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 143, '', '', 'no', 'minecraft, server, tekkit, join', '[Quick-Edit]', ''),
