(2, 46, 73, 'Aww, that sucks to hear.  Oh well, I guess we''ll have to find some way to do something about it.  It sucks. :(', '2013-06-15 00:57:40'),
(3, 16, 78, 'Who is the planned MC host you have in mind?', '2013-07-24 15:58:44'),
(4, 2, 89, 'hey everyone, sorry about the delay on tekkit server i have been very sick. I am looking to have it up before the end of the weekend i am having to re upload the world and get mods on the new server so we can have it up and running. When i get it up and there are no problems i will release the ip and everything for it. \r\n\r\nThanks for the patience ', '2014-01-23 16:46:50'),
(5, 1, 90, 'Thanks Mike.', '2014-01-25 14:26:34'),
